Unhandled promise rejection in find widget when disposed while still opened  , The find widget's update history is wrapped in a delayer promise which can cause an unhandled promise rejection when the widget is getting disposed of if the delayer's completion promise hasn't been cleanup up. This can happen if the editor is closed before the find widget has time to finish closing
